summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 2505, entitled "An Ordinance to license and regulate hawkers and peddlers", approved December 23, 1892, and Ordinance No. 3738, entitled "An Ordinance to amend Ordinance No. 2505, entitled, "An Ordinance to license and regulate hawkers and peddlers", approved December 23rd, 1892", approved March 26, 1895.
